---
globs: *.ts
alwaysApply: false
---

- Use kebab-case for file names (e.g. `api-chunk.ts`)
- For `shared/`, `#src/`, `#<any>` use workspace imports (e.g. `import env from "shared/src/env.js"`;)
- Use `import assert from 'node:assert/strict'` for type narrowing instead of `as` and `!.` TS operators.
